AI Agent API (OpenAI Agents SDK)
Overview

In this file, I built a simple AI Agent API using FastAPI and the OpenAI Agents SDK.
The agent answers user questions using the Gemini model through an OpenAI-compatible API.

What the API Does

User sends a question to the API.

The AI agent processes the query.

The Gemini model generates a response.

The API returns the AI-generated answer.

Endpoint
POST /ask

Example request:
{
  "question": "Explain memory management in Python"
}

Goal

The goal of this project was to understand how to:

Use the OpenAI Agents SDK

Integrate LLM models

Build a simple AI backend service